org.cyclops.integrateddynamics.api.network

Interface IPartNetwork

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ILazyExpressionValueCache
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PartNetwork

    public interface IPartNetwork
extends ILazyExpressionValueCache
    A network capability that can hold parts. Note that this network only contains references to the relevant data, it does not contain the actual information.

        Type Parameters:
        V - The value.
        Parameters:
